                        <interp inst="t18381022-name-1251" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE MATTHEWS</persName>
                  </hi>, <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I have not the least doubt that the prisoner is the person—I doubted his brother, and would not swear to him, but this one I can swear to.</p>
